data.name: d_infoLabel.Text
data.value:
Hello user, and thank you for using Jake_Guy_11’s Silver Assistant! This application is still in its early versions so please read this page in its entirety to learn how to use it properly.
You can go through the other tabs and select the 'help' button to find out how to properly use each feature.
To hide this application, minimize it. The icon and app will disapear, but will continue to run in the background. Notifications will continue even when the app is hidden. To show or close the application, you can find the app icon in the system tray, right click, and select what you would like to do.
Finally, please keep in mind that this is a small application created by one student, so it may be a little buggy. Thank you for downloading, enjoy!
